net.rptools.maptool.model.MacroButtonPro.toolTip:
Returns an array of all skills or the requested skill, if a name is provided.

arg(0) = toon
optional: arg(1) = skillName

returns
ex.
[
	{
    "name": "Acrobatics",
    "ability": "dex",
    "valueId": "3",
    "bonuses":     [
            {
        "type": "Magic",
        "value": 0
      },
            {
        "type": "Misc",
        "value": 0
      },
            {
        "type": "Proficiency",
        "value": 0
      },
            {
        "type": "Ability",
        "value": 2
      },
            {
        "type": "Override",
        "value": -1
      }
    ],
    "proficient": "",
    "totalBonus": -1
  }
]
